OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FI have created an exciting new
OL,7,Fpolitical credo for our time:
OL,8,FArsenalism.
OL,10,FThis is a place-based, radical set of
OL,11,Fpolicies for the regeneration of the
OL,12,FUK, or at least one important part of
OL,13,Fit, after 22 years of hurt. And it has
OL,14,Fthree central tenets.
OL,16,FThe promotion and celebration of
OL,17,Fdiversity both within the operating
OL,18,Fteam and the stakeholders, often
OL,19,Freferred to as fans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FA fundamental belief that any London
OL,7,Fpostcode area that begins with the
OL,8,Fletter "N" is innately superior.
OL,10,FAnd a patriotic celebration of those
OL,11,Fwho habitually risk their lives by
OL,12,Fscaling lampposts while singing "North
OL,13,FLondon Forever".
OL,15,FThe question you are doubtless asking
OL,16,Fis "why choose Peston's Arsenalism
OL,17,Fover Andrew Burnham's Manchesterism?"
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@JO]tD@aOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FPerhaps the most relevant point is
OL,7,Fthat Burnham is only trying to correct
OL,8,F18 years of British economic
OL,9,Funderperformance, compared with red
OL,10,FNorth London's lean years that precede
OL,11,Fthe global financial crisis by a full
OL,12,Ffour years.
OL,14,FI will give you that Burnham is not in
OL,15,Fother respects lacking in ambition. He
OL,16,Fwants to shift the very locus of power
OL,17,Ffrom Westminster to a new "Downing
OL,18,FStreet North" in Manchester that would
OL,19,Fbe "the nerve centre for a rewired
OL,20,FBritain".
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FHe said this new twin hub of an
OL,7,Fenlarged office of the prime minister
OL,8,Fwould "coordinate all parts of
OL,9,Fgovernment, at national and local
OL,10,Flevel, to agree a long-term economic
OL,11,Fstrategy and help all places set new
OL,12,Fgrowth ambitions. It will be given a
OL,13,Fmission to strive for equivalent
OL,14,Fliving conditions in all parts of
OL,15,FBritain - borrowing from the German
OL,16,FBasic Law."
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FI'll give him that one of the UK's
OL,7,Fmost intractable economic flaws is the
OL,8,Fyawning gap in wealth, income and
OL,9,Fpower between London and most of the
OL,10,Frest of the country.
OL,12,FAnd narrowing that gap - as Andy
OL,13,FHaldane has argued for more than a
OL,14,Fdecade, and is seemingly being heard
OL,15,Fproperly at the top of Labour - would
OL,16,Flift up the national economy very
OL,17,Fsubstantially, so long as it is
OL,18,Fachieved by faster growth outside
OL,19,FLondon rather than slower decline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FBut you may have perhaps noticed a
OL,7,Fpossible internal contradiction in
OL,8,FBurnham's mechanism for narrowing the
OL,9,Fnorth/south divide, namely that he is
OL,10,Fintent on stripping power from most
OL,11,FWestminster departments and
OL,12,Ftransferring those powers to mayors
OL,13,Fand local government, except in one
OL,14,Fimportant instance.
OL,16,FThe exception will be the office of
OL,17,Fthe prime minister itself. It would be
OL,18,Fsignificantly enlarged by Burnham and
OL,19,Flocated in both London and Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FSo the members of his cabinet will no
OL,7,Flonger be all-powerful barons with
OL,8,Farmies and huge fiefdoms. They will be
OL,9,Fcoordinators and facilitators - parish
OL,10,Fvicars rather than field marshals.
OL,12,FBy contrast, the King of the North, A.
OL,13,FBurnham himself, would become a smart
OL,14,Fcasual emperor, with a court that will
OL,15,Fprocess north and south.
OL,17,FThere is another possible internal
OL,18,Fcontradiction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FOn the one hand, Burnham has
OL,7,Fendeavoured to reassure nervous
OL,8,Flenders to the UK by committing to
OL,9,F"the stability that comes from sound
OL,10,Fpublic finances...and the discipline
OL,11,Fof our current fiscal rules".
OL,13,FBut he also said: "We will ensure all
OL,14,Fparts of the UK are able to take
OL,15,Fgreater public control of essential
OL,16,Fservices like water, housing, energy
OL,17,Fand transport" and "No 10 North will
OL,18,Foversee the biggest council house
OL,19,Fbuilding programme since the post-war
OL,20,Fperiod."
OL,26,@uD@SOUyD@NO]yD@TOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis actually sounds more like the
OL,12,FManchesterCityism of Pep and his
OL,13,Fpredecessors than some new form of
OL,14,FManchesterism: that is, insist you are
OL,15,Ffollowing rules that limit
OL,16,Fexpenditure, but find a way to spend
OL,17,Fhuge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FTo be clear, there may be uncertainty
OL,7,Faround what public control of
OL,8,Futilities would entail in a direct
OL,9,Ffiscal sense, at least in the next few
OL,10,Fyears, but there can be very little
OL,11,Fambiguity about the "biggest council
OL,12,Fhouse building programme" since WW2:
OL,13,Fthat would mean funding the
OL,14,Fconstruction of at least 250,000
OL,15,Fhouses a year.
OL,17,FSuch would cost significantly more
OL,18,Fthan Manchester City's entire midfield
OL,19,Fand strike force.
OL,26,@sD@UOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FMarket's and the Office for Budget
OL,7,FResponsibility might be minded to
OL,8,Fpenalise Burnham more harshly than the
OL,9,FPremier League has seen fit to punish
OL,10,FManchester City to date.
OL,12,FOr maybe not.
OL,14,FThe true assessment of Manchesterism
OL,15,Fversus Arsenalism will be in the
OL,16,Fdetail, rather than the bold big ideas.
OL,18,FThose may be some time in the making.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782800291
OL,3,CPeston: Burnham's Manchesterism versus
OL,4,Cmy Arsenalism
OL,6,FIn the short term, Burnham has
OL,7,Fchanneled the zeitgeist by offering
OL,8,Fhope. And if he's lucky, he'll have
OL,9,Fthe summer to trade on that hope until
OL,10,Fthe harsh reality of the new season
OL,11,Farrives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
